Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战从现在起进入第三阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体作战人员请根据作战时刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好发舰准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全员通话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将出发前往夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被维甘抢占的原联邦军月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰队的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开待机轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成机动战士空降作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神辅助系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮双向通信系统确认正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘也许是十恶不赦的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能听见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在火星圈痛苦挣扎的人们的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯队 开始出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧的防御火力分布图靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队可以提供的炮击也极为有限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这样 也要在敌人作出应对前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占领登陆阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 阿比斯队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cnanche Custom 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会帮我 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达AGE-FX 出发
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTA-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:34.76,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,800)}（一个月前）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来摆脱月亮二号的追兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝也完好无损的到手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么值得担心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是亲儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了维甘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又能怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么扔下我和妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论有什么理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不回来让我们放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是伊泽尔坎特侵略地球的真正目的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他说要选出优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们移居地球 建立伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他简直是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他说这是拯救人类的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球和维甘的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经走到无可挽回的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在只有做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护自己最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 要记得好好刷牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再也见不到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐接下来要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个也要保重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 温蒂也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛诺克 按计划抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤诺亚姑姑 温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3个月没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 姑姑担心死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该先跟这个人说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 你这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三年不见了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得和骨架一起换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不可能修成原来那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没打算把它修成原来那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接进化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进化成新的高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你为什么要去当宇宙海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言难尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年前 在战斗中身负重伤的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被宇宙海盗救起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养伤期间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起和海盗们共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的生活让我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争中隐藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指信息胶囊里提到的EXA-DB吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是不仅限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有迫使维甘走上战争之路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的残酷现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从得知这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法单纯地把维甘视为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想去当置身事外的海盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 我找到了适合我的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫适合你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为保护大家而战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 站在一方的立场攻击对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后真的能守护心爱的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 战斗是无法避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果让两者的力量趋于均衡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走维甘和联邦军执行作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所需的重要战略物资和情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止大规模战斗的爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我作为海盗力所能及的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要地球和维甘的实力均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争就会陷入胶着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有大量的牺牲者出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够让吉欧和罗玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所爱的那些人享受和平的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是痴人说梦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天不扑灭那些杀戮成性的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一天没有和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有在这场战争中胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把维甘斩草除根一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道您会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法和父亲不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用我的方式去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 我现在得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还会见面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你身体无恙就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要做这么全面的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不了解他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难保不会在你身体上做什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还须检查是否受到火星疫病的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘可能不像爷爷说得那样 都是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论出于什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们夺走了我们许多最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的人们也有苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让战争早日结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…到底被他们灌输了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信这是维甘奇怪行动的原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以战争为借口 选出所谓优秀人种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把弱小者逐渐淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的无非是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只以消灭对方为目的的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是正确的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论究竟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特是个疯狂的独裁者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他指挥下的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了是可憎的敌国以外什么都不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作战的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回月面上遗留的原联邦基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地曾经是联邦在月面的一大据点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在联邦主力被大量遣往地球支援的间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不慎落入敌手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地司令官 阿隆·西蒙斯叛变投敌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时有相当数量的间谍渗透进入基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在维甘发起攻击的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地内的潜伏人员发动叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的兵力几乎全军覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的月球基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敌人利用作为进攻地球的补给站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我们曾接到命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让天神号前往月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来这可能也是敌人的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为阻止维甘进一步威胁地球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定将夺回月神基地的作战计划付诸实施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西想给我看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高达吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据AGE-3在火星圈的战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统设计出的新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现前所未有的高速移动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体进行了大幅轻量化改造
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还追加了X-R专用小型支援部件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 最新型的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-FX
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-FX？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FX即是 X-R辅助型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门为跟上X-R的战斗能力而设计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把它简单理解成最强机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台高达的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以精确瞄准敌人机动战士的某个部分吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然取决于机师的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但机体确实有这种潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能够实现我想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快和敌人接火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 高达
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…到底想把我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出求救信号 等候营救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近月面 准备着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮 展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也是人 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我会坚持我战斗的方式直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 准备等离子潜航导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次出击 我心里一直有个疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被禁止使用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁同意搭载它们上船的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这征得了艾伦格雷亚斯总司令的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那东西的威力太大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 您打算把基地一起毁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是遵从章程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心存疑问的话可以去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手歼灭维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到一个不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动过于单调会被吃透的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地上出现高热源反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人高热源反应 消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是无谋 鲁莽的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有多少成功的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会陪着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再需要隐藏身份的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不再需要自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 真打算不杀敌人结束战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿 离月面着陆不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持警惕上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 即将进入月球战斗空域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这到底是吹得哪阵风？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地如果不能重回联邦之手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者的均衡就会被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘会源源不绝地向地球圈输送兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是多么庞大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是我杞人忧天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多敌人机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正降落基地周边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这样的大部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的驻守兵力足以应付
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 你本可以躲起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入近距离防御系统火力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防御系统 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在这里做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派D区3架前往掩护巴鲁德队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后续部队 不许掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我瞧瞧 你的真本领
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来需要托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了 高达
